關OpenStack https://github.com/openstack/fuel-docs/blob/master/pages/operations/how-to-shutdown-cluster-ops.rst , https://docs.mirantis.com/openstack/fuel/fuel-7.0/operations.html#howto-shut-down-the-whole-cluster
1. 關所有VM
1.1 關cf Job (用bosh stop 命令 , 順序參考 https://docs.pivotal.io/pivotalcf/customizing/start-stop-vms.html#stop)
1.1.1 bosh stop loggregator_trafficcontroller_z1
1.1.2 bosh stop loggregator_z1
1.1.3 bosh stop doppler_z1
1.1.4 bosh stop runner_z1 0
1.1.5 bosh stop runner_z1 1
1.1.6 bosh stop uaa_z1
1.1.7 bosh stop clock_global
1.1.8 bosh stop hm9000_z1
1.1.9 bosh stop router_z1
1.1.10 bosh stop ha_proxy_z1
1.1.11 bosh stop api_z1
1.1.12 bosh stop postgres_z1
1.1.13 bosh stop api_worker_z1
1.1.14 bosh stop nfs_z1
1.1.15 bosh stop etcd_z1
1.1.16 bosh stop nats_z1
1.1.17 bosh stop consul_z1
1.1.18 bosh stop stats_z1
1.2 關microbosh VM (用Horizon Dashboard)
1.3 關cf VM (用Horizon Dashboard)
1.4 關ldap VM (用Horizon Dashboard)
2. 關所有實體主機 (with clicking poweroff button or running poweroff command)
2.1 關compute nodes && cinder/ceph/swift
2.2 關controller && neutron nodes

開OpenStack https://github.com/openstack/fuel-docs/blob/master/pages/operations/how-to-shutdown-cluster-ops.rst , https://docs.mirantis.com/openstack/fuel/fuel-7.0/operations.html#howto-shut-down-the-whole-cluster
1. 開所有實體主機
1.1 開controller && neutron nodes
1.2 開compute nodes && cinder/ceph/swift
2. 開所有VM

https://groups.google.com/a/cloudfoundry.org/forum/#!topic/bosh-users/Jx4CQmH8RaA
https://bosh.io/docs/init-openstack.html
https://github.com/cloudfoundry/docs-bosh/blob/master/resurrector.html.md.erb
1. With vi, to change property 'hm.resurrector_enabled' (true -> false)
2. With bosh-init, to disable microbosh's resurrector (bosh-init deploy microbosh.yml)
3. With bosh, to stop cf's job and shutdown vm (bosh stop <job> --hard)
